quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,Alif laam meem
  2,2,Iss kitab (kay Allah ki kitab honey) mein koi shak nahi perhezgaron ko raah dikhaney wali hai
  2,3,Jo log ghaib per eman latay hain aur namaz ko qaeem rakhtay hain aur humaray diye huye (maal) mein say kharach kertay hain
  2,4,Aur jo log eman latay hain uss per jo aap ki taraf utara gaya aur jo aap say pehlay utara gaya aur woh aakhirat per bhi yaqeen rakhtay hain
  2,5,Yehi log apney rab ki taraf say hidayat per hain aur yehi log falah aur nijat paney walay hain
  2,6,Kafiron ko aap ka darana ya na darana barabar hai yeh log eman na layen gay
  2,7,Allah Taalaa ney inn kay dilon per aur inn kay kanon per mohar laga di hai aur inn ki aankhon per parda hai aur inn kay liye bara azab hai